Waxaa la ogaaday in kororka cytokine-ka uu yahay falcelin aad u daran oo ka timaada unugyada difaaca jirka ee SARS iyo MERS.
Cytokine waa nooc ka mid ah noocyada cytokine-ka ee ay ka mid yihiin TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-ka waxay kiciyaan unugyada difaaca jirka inay soo saaraan noocyo kala duwan oo xagjir ah kuwaas oo inta badan keena ARDS iyo waxyeelo xubnaha.
Ka hortagga jirka ayaa muhiim u ah in la badbaadiyo cytokines, gaar ahaan dadka qaba cudurrada halista ah.
Kortikosteroid iyo tocilizumab, oo ah IL6-ka difaaca jirka, ayaa loo isticmaalay in lagu daweeyo cytokine-ka.
Daawooyinka kale ee cytokine-ka ee difaaca jirka waxaa ka mid ah T-cell-ka la xiriira unugyada difaaca jirka; IFN-γ, IL-1, iyo TNF; JAK inhibition; blinatumomab; cytokine-ka 4 ee muujinaya; iyo HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, sida immunosuppressants, ayaa si weyn loogu isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo xanuunka.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, steroids-ka qiyaasta sare leh ayaa muhiim u ahaa dhaawaca sambabka ee dadka qaba SARS iyo COVID-19.
