2019-20 Coronavirus Pandemic waa cudurka faafa ee coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kaas oo ka dhashay cudurka neefsashada ee coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Cudurka ayaa laga helay magaalada Whuhan, Shiinaha, bishii Diseembar 2019, wuxuu noqday xaalad caafimaad oo degdeg ah 30-kii Janaayo 2020, waxaana loo aqoonsaday inuu yahay cudur faafa 11-kii Maarso 2020.
Bishii Abriil 10, 2020, 1.61 milyan oo qof ayaa la sheegay inay qabaan COVID-19 oo ku baahsan 210 dal iyo gobol, taasoo keentay 97,000 oo dhimasho.
364,000 oo qof baa badbaaday.
