Si loo xakameeyo cudurka, WHO waxay u dirtay koox Iran si ay u baarto xaaladda. Bishii Febraayo 28, saraakiisha WHO waxay ku dhawaaqeen khatarta caalamiga ah ee coronavirus inay tahay mid aad u sareysa laakiin ay tahay inay noqoto mid aad u sareysa, heerka ugu sarreeya ee taxaddarka iyo khatarta.
