Angiotensin conversion enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku jira dhinaca dibadda ee unugyada (membranes) sambabada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo xididdada.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa isbedelka angiotensin-in-enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa tirada angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista ang ((1-7) taasoo ka dhigaysa daawo awood badan oo lagu daaweeyo cudurka wadnaha. ACE2 sidoo kale waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu soo galo fayraska corona.
Enzyme-ka jidhka bini'aadamka waxaa lagu magacaabaa hACE2.
Angiotensin conversion enzyme 2 waa metallogenzyme oo ku jira zinx-ka korkiisa iyo unugyada kale ee jirka.
Borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo C-terminal oo qaadashada sanka ku qaadata amino acid.
ACE2 waxay samaysaa nooc ka mid ah dabiiciga ah ee loo yaqaan 'membrane type' oo keliya, iyadoo shaqadeeda ay tahay in ay u sameysato enzymes ka baxsan unugyada iyo maqaarka.
