ACE waxay ku xirtaa hormoonka angiotensin I iyo vasoconstriction of angiotensin II.
ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay amino acid-ka carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) waxayna ku koobantahay angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH) oo ah midka dheereeya.
