Marka la eego borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 waa meesha ugu horeysa ee lagu galo unugyada coronavirus, iyo sidoo kale HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus kaas oo SARS ka yimid); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus kaas oo COVID-19 ka yimid).
