Tirada cudurrada faafa iyo tirada dhimashada ayaa ku kala duwan ragga iyo dumarka.
Tirada dilka ragga ayaa ka badan tirada dumarka ee daraasadaha lagu sameeyay Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga.
Khatarta waxay korodhay ragga da'doodu tahay 50 sano, halka heerka ragga iyo dumarka ay ku xidhnaayeen da'doodu tahay 90 sano.
Shiinaha, heerka dhimashada waxay ahayd 2.8 boqolkiiba ragga iyo 1.7 boqolkiiba dumarka.
Sababta ay u kala duwan yihiin ragga iyo dumarka lama oga, laakiin waxaa laga yaabaa inay tahay mid ay ku jiraan hiddo-wadaha iyo dabeecadaha.
Kala duwanaanshaha difaaca ee jinsiga, isticmaalka sigaarka ee dumarka iyo ragga iyo kororka xaaladaha cudurka dilaaga sida cadaadiska dhiigga ee da'da yar ee dumarka ayaa laga yaabaa inay ka sii badan yihiin ragga.
Yurub, 57% dadka cudurka qaba waxay ahaayeen rag iyo 72% dadka u dhintay COVID-19 waxay ahaayeen rag.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, dowladda Mareykanka ma aysan sameyn tirakoob ku saabsan tirakoobka COVID-19.
Cilmi baaris ayaa muujisay in cudurrada fayraska sida Ebola, HIV, hargabka iyo SARS ay si kala duwan u saameeyaan ragga iyo dumarka.
Tirada sii kordheysa ee shaqaalaha caafimaadka, gaar ahaan kalkaaliyayaasha, waa haween, taas oo ah khatarta sare ee ku wajahan fayraska.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku dhawaaqay 11 Febraayo 2020 in magaca rasmiga ah ee cudurku uu noqon doono "COVID-19".
Madaxa WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ayaa sharaxay in CO ay tahay corona, VI ay tahay virus, D ay tahay cudur, iyo 19 markii ugu horreysay ee faafitaanka la ogaado: 31 Diseembar 2019.
Intii lagu guulaysan lahaa in la diido calaamadaha faraha ee aagga juquraafi ahaan loo yaqaan (tusaale ahaan Shiinaha), noocyada ama bulshada, taxanaha taariikhiga ah ee lagu soo bandhigay dhammaan waddamada si loo magacaabo calaamadaha ayaa ka hortagaya astaanta. Fayraska keena COVID-19 waxaa loo yaqaan 'coronavirus respiratory syndrome 2' (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO waxay sii waday inay isticmaasho "virus COVID-19" iyo "virus responsible for COVID-19" si ay u bixiso macluumaadka bulshada.
Labada cudur iyo fayras waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan "coronavirus".
Markii ugu horreysay ee cudurku ka dillaacay Wuhan, Shiinaha, fayraska iyo cudurka waxaa loo yaqaan "coronavirus" iyo "Wuhan coronavirus".
Bishii Janaayo 2020, WHO waxay soo jeedisay in 2019-nCov iyo 2019-nCoV noocyada cudurka neefsashada ee la yiraahdo respiratory infection-associated diseases (SAID) ay yihiin magacyada la filayo ee fayraska iyo cudurka ka dib markii la soo saaray 2015 marka loo eego magaca la doortay ee fayraska iyo fayraska.
Magacyada rasmiga ah ee COVID-19 iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la soo bandhigay 11 Febraayo 2020.
Marka laga reebo heerarka soo saarista qalabka caafimaadka, qaar ka mid ah soo saarayaasha qalabka dhijitaalka ah ayaa daabacaya qalabka isbitaalka sida gogosha sanka iyo qaybaha neefsashada.
Tusaale ahaan, markii isbitaal Talyaani ah uu si deg deg ah ugu baahnaa waalka hawo-qaadista, shaqaalaheeda ma aysan awoodin inay soo diraan waqtiga la rabay, shirkad maxalli ah ayaa dib u naqshadeysay oo daabacday 100 waalka oo la raadinayay hal habeen.
Ka dib markii uu bilowday faafitaanka COVID-19, aragtiyo shirqool iyo warar been abuur ah oo ku saabsan asalka, baaxadda, ka hortagga, daaweynta iyo arrimaha kale ee cudurku si weyn ayey ugu faafayeen internetka.
Dadka ayaa la ogaaday inay leeyihiin taariikh fayras u gudbinaya xayawaanka kale.
Daraasadu waxay ku guuldareysatay inay ogaato calaamadaha dhalmada fayraska ee doofaarka, bakaylaha, iyo kuwa kale.
Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal la oggolaaday in lagu daaweeyo cudurka.
Cilmi baaris caalami ah oo ku saabsan tallaalada iyo kiisaska COVID-19 ayaa waxaa bilaabay in ay sameeyaan ururada dowladda, ururada cilmi baarista iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha.
Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa bilaabay "Tijaabada SOLIDARITY" si loo baaro saameynta daaweynta anti-virus-ka ee isku dhafan taas oo muujineysa rajo weyn oo ah caawimaad.
Weli ma jiro tallaal, laakiin hay'ado badan ayaa dadaal ugu jira in la horumariyo tallaal la aqbali karo.
Daraasadaha hore ee loo sameeyay SARS-CoV waxay ku saleysan yihiin in labadaba SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 ay isticmaalaan ACE2 receptor si ay u galaan unugyada bini'aadamka.
Waxaa jira saddex istiraatiijiyad oo tallaal ah oo la raadinayo.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay soo jeediyeen in la sameeyo tallaal ka hortag ah fayraska oo dhan.
Isticmaalka fayraska noocan ah, ha ahaado mid jilicsan ama mid dhimasho leh, ayaa isku dayaya inuu si dhakhso leh u fududeeyo jawaabta difaaca jirka ee cudurka cusub ee COVID-19.
Istaraatiijiyad labaad, tallaalka subunit, ayaa ah in la sameeyo tallaal kaas oo dareemaya nidaamka difaaca jirka ee subunit-ka dhabta ah ee fayraska.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, baaritaanka noocan oo kale ah wuxuu diiradda saarayaa borotiinka spicule-S kaas oo ka caawiya fayraska inuu galo ACE2 receptor enzyme.
Istaraatiijiyad saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA, tiknoolajiyad cusub oo lagu horumarinayo tallaalka).
Tallaalada la tijaabiyay iyadoo la adeegsanayo istiraatiijiyaddan waa in la tijaabiyaa amniga iyo waxtarka isticmaalka. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, tijaabadii ugu horreysay ee tallaalka ee kiliinikada ayaa laga bilaabay afar shaqaale oo iskaa wax u qabso ah oo ku yaal Seattle.
Tallaalka waxaa ku jira in aan la soo koobi karin koodhka hidde-wadaha ee cudurka ka yimaada fayraska aadanaha. Kordhinta awoodda antibody-ku-xiran ayaa la tixgeliyey in ay ka hortagto weerarka ay noqon karto horumarinta tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin tani weli waa arrin la isku halleyn karo.
In ka badan 300 oo tijaabooyin caafimaad ayaa socda ilaa Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu baaray daaweynta la oggolaaday ee duumada, afar kalena waxay ku baareen hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska ayaa soo bandhigay sabab kale oo ay ugu wacan tahay daraasadaha Shiinaha, iyadoo sagaal tijaabooyin marxaladda III ah oo remdesivir ah ay ka socdaan dalal badan oo soo bandhigi doona dhamaadka Abriil.
Qiimaynta dhaqdhaqaaqa horumarinta kiliinikada ee tallaalka COVID-19 ee la oggol yahay ayaa la gaarey Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo ka hortagga fayraska ah ayaa loo baaray daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo la isku daray interferon beta.
Calaamadaha wanaagsan ee remdesivir ayaa la arkay bishii Maarso 2020.
Faa'iidooyinka caafimaad ee kor u kaca ayaa lagu arkay bukaanada la daweeyey remdesivir.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee wajiga III ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo markii hore loo adeegsaday daaweynta duumada, ayaa lagu baaray Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, iyadoo la helay natiijooyin horudhac ah.
Hase ahaatee, waxaa laga yaabaa in aqoonyahannadu ay ka faa'iidaystaan waxyaabaha laga helay.
Mas'uuliyiinta caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa soo saaray warqad ku saabsan isticmaalka chloroquine.
Machadka Virology ee Wuhan, marka la siiyo hal qiyaas oo gamma ah maalin kasta, waxay ku talineysaa laba qiyaasood oo ka badan inay yihiin kuwo aad u daran oo dhimasho ah.
28kii Maarso 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay oggolaansho degdeg ah oo loogu talagalay hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine si qarsoodi ah dhakhaatiirta la daweeyay ee la daweeyay bukaannada COVID-19. Nooca 7 ee Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale lagu daray interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si loo dilo COVID-19.
Xogta hore waxay muujineysaa in qiyaasta sare ee ribavirin ay muhiim u tahay in lagu xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide waxaa loo gudbiyay daraasadaha in vivo ee soo socda ka dib markii la muujiyay heerar hoose oo xakameyn ah oo SARS-CoV-2 ah. Daraasadaha ayaa muujinaya in soo-saarka qaab-dhismeedka borotiinka asalka ah ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane serine protein 2' (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay soo-saarka SARS-CoV-2 ee is-dhexgalka ACE2.
Daraasadaha ku saabsan chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo leh ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaadyo aad u daran taas oo keentay in ururka dawooyinka ay diidaan daaweynta iyada oo aan la baarin daraasadaha dambe. Oseltamivir ma aha mid ka hortagga SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana laha wax saameyn ah oo la yaqaan ee daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa xanuunka ugu daran ee marxaladda dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Tilmaamaha ayaa muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyin ka hortagga cytokine. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu soo bandhigay daawooyinka kaabayaasha ee Komishanka Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii la dhammaystiray daraasad yar.
Waxaa hadda laga wadaa tijaabo aan kala sooc lahayn oo heer qaran ah oo wajiga 2aad ah oo ka socda Talyaaniga ka dib markii natiijooyin wanaagsan laga muujiyay dadka qaba xaalado halis ah.
Waxaa lagu daraa baaritaanka serum ferritin si loo ogaado, taas oo loo sameeyay in lagu xakameeyo koritaanka, taas oo loo maleynayo inay tahay sababta ugu badan ee dhimashada inta badan dadka qaba cudurka.
Qaadashada interleukin-6 waxaa lagu ansixiyay FDA dhammaan daraasadaha la soo dhaafay ee daaweynta cudurka cytokine-refractory steroidal syndrome oo lagu sameeyay sabab kale, CAR T-cell therapy, 2017.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah, ma jiro tijaabo la isugu xigtay oo la xakameyn karo oo lagu kalsoonaan karo in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn dhab ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
Bixinta unugyada difaaca jirka ee la nadiifiyey iyo koontaroolayaasha laga helay nidaamka difaaca ee dadka ka badbaaday COVID-19 ee loo gudbiyo dadka u baahan ayaa la soo jeediyay inay noqoto habka tallaalka la'aanta ah ee tallaalka.
Qalabkan oo kale ayaa la tijaabiyey laakiin waxtar ma lahayn.
Xakamaynta fayraska ayaa ah habka la filayo in daaweynta unugyada difaaca ee aan waxyeello gaarin ay ku yareyn karto difaaca SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale, sida cytotoxicity iyo/ama phagocytosis ee unugyada ku tiirsan antibody ayaa laga yaabaa inay shaqeeyaan.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibody-ka ee aan la isticmaalin, tusaale ahaan, isticmaalka antibody-ka monoclonic-ka ee la sameeyay, ayaa la horumarinayaa.
Qeybta keydinta serum-ka ee bukaanada ka badbaaday cudurka, oo ah qayb ka mid ah dareeraha dhiigga ee ka soo jeeda dadka ka badbaaday iyo kuwa leh unugyada difaaca ee ku takhasusay fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo kala saaro si dhakhso leh.
